OL,3,CMan charged with murder of 'beloved'
OL,4,Cmother
OL,6,FA man is due to appear in court
OL,7,Fcharged with the murder of a "beloved"
OL,8,Fmother in Leeds.
OL,10,FJack Johns, 52, was charged overnight
OL,11,Fon Monday in connection with the death
OL,12,Fof 51-year-old Gosia Wiktor.
OL,14,FMs Wiktor was found seriously injured
OL,15,Fon Thursday, 11 June, at an address on
OL,16,FFoster Square in the Belle Isle area
OL,17,Fof the city, where she later died.
OL,19,FJohns was taken to the hospital in a
OL,20,Fcritical condition, where he was
OL,21,Farrested.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/2
